metadata.name: Blue Moon
metadata.description:
At the appointed time, a C-4 bomb was detonated. Black smoke billowed out with the sound of the explosion.
The media would expose the whole thing if it became so important.

"...... Mission complete. Escaping via Route A as planned."

The girl broke through the glass on the upper floor and ran outside.
She left the facility with its burning smell and disappeared into the bustle of the night.
